714864f-a.title: Manhattan: 95th Street (East) - 5th Avenue
714864f-a.text:
3 East 95th Street, east of the N.E. corner of Fifth Avenue. This house was formerly the residence of Clarence Mackay.
About 1922.
Gift of E. M. Jenks.
Nca. ~ 2213
